Gene BUCK, as President of the American Society of Composers, etc., and Harms, Incorporated, Appellants, v. Rex De BARR, etc., Ap-pellee. No. 6410. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. March 16, 1931.

Before RUDKIN, WILBUR, and SAW-TELLE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Pursuant to stipulation of counsel for the respective parties, ordered appeal dismissed ; mandate forthwith.
